Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.03,0:00:12.16,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,This day is going to be perfect
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.53,0:00:16.45,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The kind of day of which I've dreamed since I was small
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.24,0:00:19.28,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All those armor loving bores
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.32,0:00:21.28,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Say I look great in uniform
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.66,0:00:25.74,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,What they don't know is that I have fooled them all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.45,0:00:29.66,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,This day was going to be perfect
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.12,0:00:33.99,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The kind of day of which I've dreamed since I was small
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.74,0:00:36.66,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But instead of having cake
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.78,0:00:38.91,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,With all my friends to celebrate
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.03,0:00:42.78,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,My wedding bells may never ring for me at all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.99,0:00:45.20,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I care not a thing about the ring
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.32,0:00:47.62,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I won't partake in any cake
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.03,0:00:50.70,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Vows? Well I'll be lying when I say~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.49,0:00:53.41,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,That through any kind of weather
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.53,0:00:55.45,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I'll want us to be together
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:00:59.62,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The truth is I don't care for her at all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.82,0:01:02.78,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,No, I do not love the bride
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.91,0:01:06.62,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,For my heart is dead inside
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.87,0:01:13.20,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But I still want her to be mine
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.37,0:01:15.28,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We must escape before it's too late
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.37,0:01:17.53,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Find a way to save the day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.82,0:01:20.57,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Hope? I'd be lying if I say~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.87,0:01:22.87,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I don't fear that I may lose her
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.95,0:01:24.62,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,To one who wants to use her
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.82,0:01:28.28,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Not care for, love and cherish her each day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.70,0:01:31.82,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,For I oh so love the bride
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.99,0:01:35.70,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Oh, in my heart she does reside
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.91,0:01:44.12,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Oh, Princess Ca~dance, I'll soon be by your side
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.16,0:01:55.37,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Finally, the moment has arrived
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.62,0:01:59.03,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,For me to take a very lucky bride
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.70,0:02:01.20,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Oh, the wedding we won't make
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.28,0:02:03.32,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,She'll end up marrying a fake
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.41,0:02:06.12,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Princess Cadance will be
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.24,0:02:06.87,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Mine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.95,0:02:08.28,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All mine